                                    "header":  "Opportunity description",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;Korean government is offering GKS\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.for9a.com/en/opportunity/category/Scholarships\"\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003eUndergraduate\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003eScholarship\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003e\u0026nbsp;for international students to study at top universities in Korea, helping them pursue academic degrees while promoting global educational exchange and fostering stronger friendships between Korea and participating nations.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"52\" data-start=\"0\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"50\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eDuration of the Korean Government Scholarship:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"86\" data-start=\"54\"\u003eThe duration varies by degree:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"298\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"88\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"157\" data-start=\"88\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"157\" data-start=\"90\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"105\" data-start=\"90\"\u003eBachelor\u0026rsquo;s:\u003c/strong\u003e 4 years, plus 1 year of Korean language training.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"225\" data-start=\"158\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"225\" data-start=\"160\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"173\" data-start=\"160\"\u003eMaster\u0026rsquo;s:\u003c/strong\u003e 2 years, plus 1 year of Korean language training.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"298\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"226\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"298\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"228\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"248\" data-start=\"228\"\u003eDoctorate (PhD):\u003c/strong\u003e 3 years, plus 1 year of Korean language training.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003carticle data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-62\" data-turn=\"assistant\" data-turn-id=\"request-6975bf0b-58d8-832f-9c22-5330f2206c0d-29\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003cdiv tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f0387d9d-af98-4f84-9e20-56e72693c302\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-5-mini\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"88\" data-start=\"0\"\u003eApplications for all programs open from \u003cstrong data-end=\"85\" data-start=\"40\"\u003elate September to the end of October 2026\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"129\" data-start=\"90\"\u003eThere are \u003cstrong data-end=\"126\" data-start=\"100\"\u003etwo application tracks\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"245\" data-start=\"130\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"160\" data-start=\"130\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"160\" data-start=\"132\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"158\" data-start=\"132\"\u003eThrough the university\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"245\" data-start=\"161\"\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"245\" data-start=\"163\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"189\" data-start=\"163\"\u003eThrough the university\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cem data-end=\"243\" data-start=\"190\"\u003e(appears repeated; possibly a typo in the original)\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"317\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"247\"\u003eEach track has \u003cstrong data-end=\"285\" data-start=\"262\"\u003edifferent deadlines\u003c/strong\u003e depending on the year and term.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003carticle data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-63\" data-turn=\"user\" data-turn-id=\"ccc1a284-4b4b-42db-9ad3-1852a268fd96\" dir=\"auto\" tabindex=\"-1\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
